net.myorb.math.specialfunctions

Class FieldOdeSolution

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.myorb.math.computational.CommonSplineDescription<java.lang.Double>
      • net.myorb.math.specialfunctions.FieldOdeSolution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Element, JsonBinding.JsonRepresentation<java.lang.Double>

    public class FieldOdeSolution
extends CommonSplineDescription<java.lang.Double>
    an attempt to demonstrate building a spline for a sequence of RK4 solution approximations. the y and yPrime exports of this class are the y(x) and y'(x) entries for calculations using the splines. see FieldSplineTest.txt for a script running precision tests on this spline as a solution to the ODE.
    Author:
    Michael Druckman
